The evidence with the title 'Obama was right, health insurance should be voluntary ... ' says 5 days ago  ... Tax filers this year who do n't acquire health insurance must pay the government a fee equal to $ 695 per adult plus $347.50 per child, or 2.5 percent of total family income  ... Yet , steep as the penalty is, millions of Americans would rather fork it over than buy medical insurance they do n't want or can't afford. 
